Wow, this was sooooo good. Don't bother with the thermometer; if I'd waited until it had hit 160 degrees I would have overcooked the custard. As it is it was too thick to strain and didn't appear to need straining anyway. Impressive tasting dessert and really not all that difficult despite the numerous steps.

