Rating: 4
I always thought making chocolate mousse was a disaster waiting to happen... not with this recipe! Despite the number of steps that had to be coordinated it came out like a dream (and all I could find for chocolate was Hershey's Special Dark.) I can't wait to try this recipe with a good European dark chocolate. I took the mousse to my Cooking Club's French night and everyone loved it. Most couldn't finish a full serving because it's so rich, but it was a hit.

